  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\nA dependency on `.../package.json`, makes it not possible to run `fault-detector` using just the dist files: `node dist/src/service.js`\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum-optimism/optimism/blob/develop/packages/fault-detector/src/service.ts#L42\r\n\r\n**Additional context**\r\n\r\n```\r\nnode:internal/modules/cjs/loader:959\r\n  throw err;\r\n  ^\r\n\r\nError: Cannot find module '../package.json'\r\nRequire stack:\r\n- /faultdetector/dist/src/service.js\r\n    at Function.Module._resolveFilename (node:internal/modules/cjs/loader:956:15)\r\n    at Function.Module._load (node:internal/modules/cjs/loader:804:27)\r\n    at Module.require (node:internal/modules/cjs/loader:1028:19)\r\n    at require (node:internal/modules/cjs/helpers:102:18)\r\n    at new FaultDetector (/faultdetector/dist/src/service.js:16:22)\r\n    at Object.<anonymous> (/faultdetector/dist/src/service.js:234:21)\r\n    at Module._compile (node:internal/modules/cjs/loader:1126:14)\r\n    at Object.Module._extensions..js (node:internal/modules/cjs/loader:1180:10)\r\n    at Module.load (node:internal/modules/cjs/loader:1004:32)\r\n    at Function.Module._load (node:internal/modules/cjs/loader:839:12) {\r\n  code: 'MODULE_NOT_FOUND',\r\n  requireStack: [ '/faultdetector/dist/src/service.js' ]\r\n}\r\n```\r\n",
